---
---

<section class="section" id="about" aria-labelledby="about-title">
  <div class="container about__inner">
    <div class="about__image-wrap">
      <img
        src="/artist.jpg"
        alt="NAMENLOS — artist portrait"
        class="about__image"
        loading="lazy"
        width="560"
        height="700"
      />
      <div class="about__image-border" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="about__text">
      <p class="section-label">About</p>
      <h2 class="section-title" id="about-title">The artist<br />behind the name</h2>

      <div class="about__bio">
        <p>
          NAMENLOS is the project of a Berlin-based sound artist who prefers to let the
          music speak for itself. Drawing from industrial, dark ambient, techno, and
          experimental traditions, the sets move between tension and release — between
          noise and silence.
        </p>
        <p>
          Each performance is composed live, responding to the room, the people, and the
          moment. No two shows are the same.
        </p>
        <p>
          Active since 2018. Releases on cassette and digital. Resident at various
          underground venues across Europe.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about__stats">
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat__number">200+</span>
          <span class="stat__label">Live sets</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat__number">15+</span>
          <span class="stat__label">Countries</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat__number">8</span>
          <span class="stat__label">Releases</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about__inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about__image-wrap {
    position: relative;
  }

  .about__image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 70vh;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: top center;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    filter: grayscale(30%);
  }

  .about__image-border {
    position: absolute;
    inset: -8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: calc(var(--radius-md) + 4px);
    pointer-events: none;
    opacity: 0.4;
  }

  .about__text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .about__bio {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
  }

  .about__stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    padding-top: var(--space-md);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }

  .stat__number {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .stat__label {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about__inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .about__image {
      height: 50vh;
    }
  }
</style>
